		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Whenever you are using 8x16 sprites, any graphics from sprites not found are taken from the right pattern table.
<br />Occasionally, you have a game that will use 8x16 sprites, and IRQs, and try to take from the left pattern table (Mario Adventure).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
